title: Unreal Engine 4.2 Compiled Installer
description:
Unreal Engine 4.2

Info
Installation Time 15-20 min (depends on your pc specs)
-Setup Size 2.55GB
-After Installation 19GB

Included
-Unreal Engine 4.2 compiled
-Direct x June 2010

Screenshots
-http://imgur.com/a/sLNhs	

What you need	
-Visual Studio 2013
-Directx june 2010 included in setup no need to download) link below
-http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=8109

Instructions
-Open shortcut on desktop or, EngineBinariesWin64UE4Editor.exe
-It will take a min or so to start up so give it time
-After it starts up it will compile the shaders which takes time

Short Version	
1. Install
2. Open shortcut
3. let it compile shaders (does it automatically)
